<h3>Discovering the Island</h3>

<p>Cyprus offers a diverse range of attractions. From the sun-kissed beaches of Ayia Napa and the rugged landscapes of Akamas Peninsula to the historic streets of Paphos and the mountainous regions of Troodos, there's much to explore. Having a rental car gives you the ease to visit these attractions on your own timetable.</p>

