<h3>Driving in Cyprus</h3>

<p>Driving in Cyprus is on the left-hand side of the road, and the road network is well-developed, particularly in major towns and along the coast. However, be cautious when driving in mountainous areas and small villages, as roads can be narrow and winding.</p>

